---
title: Honey-Thyme Pork Tenderloin with Roasted Potatoes and Broccoli
description: This cal-smart supper is full of flavour, not richness! Honey and thyme make a hearty glaze for tender pork. Easy roasted potatoes and broccoli complete this ideal week night plate.

